<p><strong>L:</strong> Student is shown into a private room by nurse and asked to take a seat on the medical examination chair stationed near the center of the room.<br />
<strong>R:</strong> Nurse takes vitals and asks patients questions relevant to their health. Nurse turns away from patient to input this information into EHR system located on desktop. Student cannot see desktop unless 21” monitor is physically turned.</p>
<figure class="l-middle">
  <div class="figure-grid">
