</figure>

<p><strong>L:</strong> When finished with examination, doctor turns away from student and inputs information into desktop EHR system. If necessary, doctor can input any necessary prescriptions or follow-up recommendations.<br />
<strong>R:</strong> The appointment concludes and student typically leaves with verbal information from doctor. Written information may come via EHR system or if doctor has provided an informational brochure from the room.</p>
